data.title: Tyson Chandler Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Tyson Chandler with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Lived and worked on a farm until age 9

Learned to play basketball on grass on a basket hung on a tree

Reached a height of 6 feet by age 10

Was a high-school teammate of Tayshaun Prince

Despite scholarship offers from numerous college powerhouses, went straight from high school to the NBA

Drafted with the second overall pick in the 2001 draft by the Los Angeles Clippers

Has played for five different teams in his 11-year career

He and his wife were active in the Hurricane Katrina relief effort

Named 2012 NBA Defensive Player of the Year as a member of the New York Knicks
